    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║     IoT Core Model Processor - Arduino + Mobile Integration      ║
    ║                                                                    ║
    ║     Reading: TEMP, HUM, LUX, SOLAR, BATT from Arduino            ║
